The course endeavours to provide an overview of Estonian literature in the period (1917-2015). Key topics include Estonian literary in the first independence period, literature in the Estonian SSR, and Estonian literature during the last 25 years.Objectives/eesmärkid:  To provide an overview of Estonian literature from 1917-2015, focusing in depth on the works of he key writers of the period.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Upon completion of the course the student 
- will know the main features of Estonian literature beginning with the group "Siuru" until the present day.
- is capable of making distinctions between the most important literary trends of the period.
- has read the most signficant texts of belles lettres in Estonian in the designated period.
